OOC: Again, sorry about that, and I have beaten my friend for not posting for 
me.  I assure you, it was most painful.  But I'm back, and more or less 
awake...

::Cygnar::
       He coughs and shakes his head.  "Err... sorry about that.  I was just 
trying to compose my thoughts...  You see, I'm a bit slow and it takes me a 
while sometimes."  He smiles innocently, well as innocently as an evil swan 
robot can.  "I hope you'll forgive me.  I'll be quite ready whenever your 
esteemed leader returns."

--part1_59.1f762594.2a81d5ff_boundary
